-- Marsh & McLennan Buys Hammond, Adds Consulting for Endowments, Foundations
-- B y   N a t a l i e   D o s s
-- 2010-11-24T17:04:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-24/marsh-mclennan-buys-hammond-adds-consulting-for-endowments-foundations.html
Marsh & McLennan Cos., the second-
largest insurance broker, agreed to buy Hammond Associates to
add consulting for clients including endowments and foundations.  The deal is expected to be completed by the end of this
year, and the unit will be part of New York-based Marsh &
McLennan’s Mercer business, the buyer said in a statement today
distributed by Business Wire. Terms weren’t disclosed.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Natalie Doss in New York at 
 ndoss@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  